description:
Knowledge and understanding of the musculo-skeletal system and its application to human movement. Application and evaluation of major movement patterns in specific sports.
This course had the previous code of HMST7386 which can be viewed in the archived area within the Course and Program site http://www.uq.edu.au/study/archive/index.html
incompatible: HMST7386 or BIOL7386; HMST2630 or 3633 or ANAT1005 or ANAT2029
